@node "Main" "HTMLtoTeX - Main"
 This is


    @{b}HTMLtoTeX Version 2.10@{ub}
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    a tool for converting HTML documents into LaTeX2e textfiles.

